text: Věra Drazdíková (born 1 February 1933) is a Czech gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1956 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:Czech female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Czechoslovakia Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Prague
